<div class='commentbox'>
Ive only had 1 chance before to catch this creek running and a shoulder injury ended that. I talked<br/>
to my friends that did do the run and they said that basically the falls were the easiest part. I<br/>
beleive the word used to describe the rest of the run (Im assuming the section below the falls) was<br/>
&quot;explosive.&quot; Granted they ran it above the recommended level (by alot I think) their<br/>
comments still reflect the character of the run. So, if you take out below the falls, you miss the<br/>
meat of the run. </div>
